MakeBigRIPSTree.C : making bigrips tree for offline event building(pre-analysis)

MakeFullBigRIPSTree.C : making bigrips tree for offline event building(pre-analysis). including tof, rips and beam information need to be checked.

MakeSiTree.C : making si stopper tree for offline event building.

CombineTS.C : macro to combine tree files: bigrips, si and ge. 

ShowTS.C : macro to check time-stamp information of a root file.

Analysis.C : a sample macro to analyze combined tree.
